Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.07,0:16:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Celty-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.74,0:16:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Tránh đường!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.10,0:16:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hôm nay mày sẽ phơi xác!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.38,0:16:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Lấy đầu Shizuo cho tao!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.27,0:16:35.46,Internet talk,,0,0,0,,Uầy, nhìn kìa!
